{"tid":2385640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍「遏制中國是Mission Impossible」 網：每集都完成任務","createTime":"2021-01-29T06:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T07:33:35.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a4a7eff0869cf4faea065a9b003b798546ff7627","tid":2385640,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:56:22.000Z","msg":"解放軍「遏制中國是Mission Impossible」 網：每集都完成任務<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D-%E9%81%8F%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%AFmission-impossible-%E7%B6%B2-%E6%AF%8F%E9%9B%86%E9%83%BD%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99-034248053.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D-%25E9%2581%258F%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2598%25AFmission-impossible-%25E7%25B6%25B2-%25E6%25AF%258F%25E9%259B%2586%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258B%2599-034248053.html&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1wx1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=bcba6a50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D-%E9%81%8F%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%AFmission-impossible-%E7%B6%B2-%E6%AF%8F%E9%9B%86%E9%83%BD%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99-034248053.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中國國防部昨（28日）下午由發言人、大校吳謙舉行例行記者會，當被問到如何看到與川普政權的關係，以及未來與拜登政權的中美兩軍關係發展，吳謙用雙語表示：<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">「遏制中國是不可能的任務，最終只會搬石頭砸了自己的腳。To Contain China, Mission Impossible！」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吳謙表示，在川普任內，中美關係嚴重困難，遇到很多風險和挑戰，不過遏制中國是「Mission Impossible」，現在兩軍重新站在新的歷史起點上，希望美國可以秉持不衝突不對抗、合作共贏的精神，加強對話，聚焦合作，管控分歧，與中國相向而行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而被問到台美關係持續深化，吳謙回應，台灣問題是中國內政，解放軍在台海地區展開的軍事活動，是針對安全形勢和維護國家主權所採取的必要行動，是對外部勢力干涉和台獨勢力挑釁的嚴正回應。「台獨分裂分子的謀獨行徑，就像是一個泡沫，又能翻得起幾朵浪花？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而對於吳謙在記者會突然秀出英文能力，有網友回應，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">「他知道每一集的Mission Impossible伊森都有完成任務嗎？」</span></span></strong>「自帶BGM的一句話」「Mission Impossible每一集的任務都在主角威能+團隊合作之下，順利地完成。」"},{"pid":"64d165f456e997ceba7ca587c8516b04d31d6c63","tid":2385640,"uid":235754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:12:47.000Z","msg":"Ethan Hunt咪美國人囉"},{"pid":"958d81a9035606c9a003e35b28f4f5f87417f91f","tid":2385640,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc45fda42b0d998b628f57af0740919d9339768","tid":2385640,"uid":367918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:23:39.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbbcbdbce33a6ea6685bba585509e919d7f64f2","tid":2385640,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c509707ba33b839eb5b847b9c29424fda86af5bb","tid":2385640,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7883f73d101da86946d49b11b5df7d4d9495a1","tid":2385640,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:26:34.000Z","msg":"凳凳凳..... 凳凳凳...... 凳凳！"},{"pid":"00d81242cc21317031dd5534